OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fperiods on Sunday but remaining dry.
OL,7,FBecoming bright and sunny on Monday
OL,8,Fand Tuesday and feeling very warm for
OL,9,Fmost, a little cooler near coasts with
OL,10,Fan onshore flow.
